Integrating TNF score and ABD score is challenging because their distributions can be very different, we therefore applied quantile normalization to TNF score using ABD score distribution. After the normalization, a composite score (S) is calculated by taking the geometric mean of TNF score and ABD score. S is subsequently used as the edge weight in the graph-based clustering (below),
